# W890-7 — user/project config + capture store. The user TOML lives at
# ~/.kolm/config.toml (HOME, not repo) but if a contributor symlinks or
# copies the file into the repo tree these globs catch it. captures.db is
# the local SQLite capture store; *.db / *.sqlite under data/ are already
# ignored, this row makes the intent for the repo root explicit.
